law.text: In his or her discretion, the commissioner may include health maintenance organizations or designated types of health maintenance organizations doing business pursuant to this subtitle in coordination of benefits guidelines prescribed pursuant to KRS 304.18-085.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1513, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 427, sec. 11, effective July 14, 2000. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 433, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1986.
